00:08:16,010 --> 00:08:19,941
[SPEAKER_05]: from Daniel Connor at 63 Tyler Avenue.

92
00:08:22,227 --> 00:08:24,448
[SPEAKER_05]: I'm a resident of the Brooks neighborhood for 10 years.

93
00:08:24,629 --> 00:08:28,251
[SPEAKER_05]: I want to express my support for maintaining the current house at 28 Grove Street.

94
00:08:28,791 --> 00:08:31,973
