141
00:12:36,390 --> 00:12:43,034
[SPEAKER_09]: So that part I was proposing to rebuild, but it will stay in the same style and the same footprint.

142
00:12:44,154 --> 00:12:59,223
[SPEAKER_09]: So in my mind, my goal is to actually make this house to shine again within its original, I would say, footprint or original style.

143
00:12:59,883 --> 00:13:06,226
[SPEAKER_09]: So I think my goal and the goal of the historic commission is pretty much aligned.

144
00:13:06,326 --> 00:13:13,269
[SPEAKER_09]: So and the current house is really in a bad shape as everyone may have chance to see it.

145
00:13:14,509 --> 00:13:22,653
[SPEAKER_09]: And from the structural engineers report, the recommendation is to have it repaired or renovated as soon as possible.

146
00:13:23,213 --> 00:13:34,100
[SPEAKER_09]: So I sincerely hope the commissioners can give me the chance to really actually make the project happen as soon as possible without further delay.

147
